---
import PageLayout from "../layouts/PageLayout.astro";
---
<PageLayout title="Privacy" description="Informativa privacy." locale="it">
  <section class="bg-paper px-8 pt-32 pb-24">
    <div class="max-w-[760px] mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-[clamp(24px,3vw,48px)] font-black tracking-[-0.04em] leading-[0.95] mb-8 text-center">Privacy.</h1>
      <p class="text-base text-ink/70 mb-4 italic">
        Documento in lavorazione. Sarà sostituito con la versione redatta da un avvocato prima del lancio commerciale.
      </p>
      <p class="text-base text-ink/70">
        Per domande contatta <a href="mailto:privacy@futugrana.com" class="underline">privacy@futugrana.com</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</PageLayout>
